1327
01:21:07,917 --> 01:21:11,330
Some idiot used
an unencrypted phone.

1328
01:21:11,458 --> 01:21:14,075
Shit.

1329
01:21:21,375 --> 01:21:23,207
All right, everyone, listen up!

1330
01:21:23,333 --> 01:21:24,539
He's coming.

1331
