1336
01:21:48,208 --> 01:21:49,664
Go! Go!

1337
01:21:52,917 --> 01:21:54,203
Come on. Come on!

1338
01:21:56,542 --> 01:21:57,542
Ready to go!

1339
01:21:58,583 --> 01:22:00,494
