match weapons missing
from Evidence,

1352
01:24:54,750 --> 01:24:56,059
and I got your prints
all over them.

1353
01:24:56,083 --> 01:24:57,824
This is bullshit.

1354
01:24:57,917 --> 01:24:58,952
I also have

1355
01:24:59,083 --> 01:25:01,040
CCTV footage of you and Vallon

1356
01:25:01,167 --> 01:25:02,498
